# Git Rules

- This repo (UsefulHQ/UsefulCRM) is a **fork** of hermes/hermes.
- When creating PRs, ALWAYS target `UsefulHQ/UsefulCRM` — never the upstream `hermes/hermes`.
  Use `gh pr create --repo UsefulHQ/UsefulCRM` to ensure this.
- NEVER commit or push without explicit user approval.
- NEVER force push to main/master.
